          Buoy finds hardcoded colors, duplicate components, and token violations.
        </p>

        <!-- CTAs -->
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-12">
          <Button href={siteConfig.githubUrl} size="lg" external>
